title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 5
description:
Dave joined us live from Miami in the midst of a hurricane and battled through his own tech issues. Who watched what games? and who came in who's hole? The race for the Pat Hill Trophy is getting tighter each week.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
